<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. بِمَا أَتَى فِيهِ مِنْ عِلْمٍ وَمِنْ حِكَمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَمَّا عَلَى مَنْ تَوَلَّى عَنْهُ فَهُوَ عَمَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لِكَوْنِهِ عَنْ هُدَاهُ الْمُسْتَنِيرُ عَمِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَمَنْ يُقِمْهُ يَكُنْ يَوْمَ الْمَعَادِ لَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>خَيْرُ الإِمَامِ إِلى الْفِرْدَوْسِ وَالنِّعَمِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>كَمَا يَسُوقُ أُولِي الأَعْرَاضِ عَنْهُ إِلى<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>دَارِ الْمَقَامِعِ وَالأَنْكَالِ وَالأَلَمِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَقَدْ أَتَى النَّصُّ فِي الطُّوْلَيْنِ أَنَّهُمَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ظِلاً لِتَالِيْهِمَا فِي مَوْقِفِ الْغَمَمِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَنَّهُ فِي غَدٍ يَأْتِي لِصَاحِبِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مُبَشِّراً وَحَجِيجاً عَنْهُ إِنْ يُقِمِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَالْمُلْكَ وَالْخُلْدَ يُعْطِيهِ وَيُلْبِسُه<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>تَاجَ الْوَقارِ الإِلهُ الْحَقُّ ذُو الْكَرَمِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>يُقَالُ اقْرَأْ وَرَتِّلْ وَارْقَ فِي غرَفِ الْـ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>جَنَّاتِ كَيْ تَنْتَهِي لِلْمَنْزِلِ النَّعِمِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَحُلَّتَانِ مِنْ الْفِرْدَوْسِ قَدْ كُسِيتْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِوَالِدَيْهِ لَهَا الأَكْوَانُ لَمْ تَقُمْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>قَالا بِمَاذَا كَسَيْنَاهَا فَقِيلَ بِمَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَقْرَأْتُمَا ابْنَكُمَا فَاشْكُرْ لِذِي النِّعَمِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>كَفَى وَحَسْبُكَ بِالْقُرْآنِ مُعْجِزةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>دَامَتْ لَدَيْنَا دَوَاماً غَيْرَ مُنْصَرِمِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>